{"tid":894402,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【東涌淪陷惹禍？】海堤灣畔劈價29% 呎價跌破1萬","createTime":"2018-11-08T11:17:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-09T02:04:26.000Z","uid":174649,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"48bda30de5999b3d0af9afd4c5b69396202b0c28","tid":894402,"uid":174649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T11:17:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181108/large/1541672128_a5ea.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181108%2Flarge%2F1541672128_a5ea.jpg&h=57eb32b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美聯物業吳惠斌表示，東涌私樓再跌穿1萬元，海堤灣畔呎價2座低層G室，雖然為低層戶，但仍有全海景，實用面積846方呎，今年9月以市價1,050萬元放售，有見樓市向下，最近把叫價調低至950萬元仍未見承接，直至剛剛減至822萬元終售出，低見9,716元，為屋苑今年呎價首跌破1萬元，形容「平過居屋」。業主於2013年10月以710萬元買入單位，5年升幅僅15%。<br />\n<br />\n同類單位對上成交要追溯至今年6月，為3座高層G室，實用面積855方呎，透過公司轉讓以1,150萬元成交，呎價13,593元，兩者相差足足29%。<br />\n<br />\n畀多單同類成交參考，1座高層B室，850方呎，今年3月成交1,074萬元，呎價12,635元。<br />\n<br />\n港珠澳大橋通車後，內地客逼爆東涌人龍處處，引發淪陷之說。吳惠斌表示，交通位置主要在東堤灣畔隔籬，東堤街坊比較感受大，唯暫未有新成交是受到有關因素影響。"},{"pid":"7554f8a7347ebb9ab3c94dc97c8f6a947a9ee4e8","tid":894402,"uid":6799,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T11:36:25.000Z","msg":"東涌唔計<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d212c076b95ff59c29ad58ce72207cde95aca58","tid":894402,"uid":171446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T11:47:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d739584ebbdd765e06613018498d305dafb008db","tid":894402,"uid":159313,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T00:45:06.000Z","msg":"有低層呢兩隻字跌幾多都唔計<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cffbb893de76fbc1a4c6ea89d7192b4f757dddb","tid":894402,"uid":28245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T01:00:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"h